---
title: Beef and Bacon Burger in Truffle Sauce with cheesy fries and tomato side salad
description: The crispy bacon and juicy beef burger in this recipe are smothered in lashings of rich and creamy truffle sauce. Chunky cheesy chips and light refreshing side salad round out a satisfying meal.
